  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot For The Stars is a physics based rage-platformer where you are a pistol.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>YOU YEARN FOR THE STARS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you stare out your window to watch the night sky, you feel you belong among them! But you must earn your place and it won't be easy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498260/extras/c2ade614fb3b34b9a0b425f888b9a901.avif?t=1747411301\" width=800 height=1036 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HOW FAR CAN YOU CLIMB?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  In this physics based rage-platformer, you move by using a combination of leveraging your barrel and your limited ammo to propel you upwards. Master precise aiming, momentum control, and recoil physics to navigate various obstacles, platforms, and heartbreaking falls. Keep an eye on your bullet count or else you may be left falling while reloading.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you make it to the stars? Or will you give up at the bottom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498260/extras/ef4e4faa02e3be6e977b301243fddfe4.poster.avif?t=1747411301\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498260/extras/ef4e4faa02e3be6e977b301243fddfe4.webm?t=1747411301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498260/extras/ef4e4faa02e3be6e977b301243fddfe4.mp4?t=1747411301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot For The Stars is a physics based rage-platformer where you are a pistol.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>YOU YEARN FOR THE STARS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you stare out your window to watch the night sky, you feel you belong among them! But you must earn your place and it won't be easy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498260/extras/c2ade614fb3b34b9a0b425f888b9a901.avif?t=1747411301\" width=800 height=1036 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HOW FAR CAN YOU CLIMB?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  In this physics based rage-platformer, you move by using a combination of leveraging your barrel and your limited ammo to propel you upwards. Master precise aiming, momentum control, and recoil physics to navigate various obstacles, platforms, and heartbreaking falls. Keep an eye on your bullet count or else you may be left falling while reloading.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you make it to the stars? Or will you give up at the bottom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498260/extras/ef4e4faa02e3be6e977b301243fddfe4.poster.avif?t=1747411301\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498260/extras/ef4e4faa02e3be6e977b301243fddfe4.webm?t=1747411301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498260/extras/ef4e4faa02e3be6e977b301243fddfe4.mp4?t=1747411301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
